data.description: Welcome to your modern oasis! This end unit townhouse, nestled in the sought-after DD2 school district, boasts brand new appliances and gas cooking for culinary enthusiasts. The open floor plan, adorned with an oversized island, creates the perfect space for gatherings of any size. Upgrades like the large stamped concrete back porch, stylish kitchen backsplash, and elegant wood steps and railing add a touch of luxury. The master bedroom is complemented with a large walk-in closet and two additional closets in the master bath to accommodate all your storage needs. The master bath shower has also been updated to a sliding glass door. This townhouse is not just a house; it's a beautiful place to call your next home!
